Package: libqzeitgeist-0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Zeitgeist - Qt 4 library
 This package contains QtZeitgeist, a Qt-based library for Zeitgeist
 service.
 .
 Zeitgeist is a service which logs the users's activities and events,
 anywhere from files opened to websites visited and conversations.

