Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libqt4-dev (>= 4.7.0),
         pkg-config (>= 0.21),
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qt 4 Zeitgeist library (headers and library)
 This package contains development files for libqzeitgeist, a Qt-based
 library for Zeitgeist service.
 .
 Zeitgeist is a service which logs the users's activities and events,
 anywhere from files opened to websites visited and conversations.
